   в”Ӯ     в”Ӯ
   в”Ӯ     в””в”Җ
   в”Ӯ
   в””в”Җ when you've truly reflected, run
      в””в”Җ rhx route.stone.set --stone 1.vision --as promised --that has-questioned-fundamentals[0m[31m[0m
